      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been maintained to the highest possible standards. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish and absolutely no chips, scratches, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition, still smelling fresh and showing zero signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with a complete service history and every component functioning exactly as it did the day it left the factory. This is a rare opportunity to own an impeccably preserved example that will satisfy even the most discerning collector.",
