    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. The exterior boasts a flawless factory finish with a deep, mirror-like luster, free of any stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in 'as-new' condition, featuring supple, uncreased leather seating and a pristine dashboard that still carries the faint aroma of a new car. Every electronic component and mechanical system operates with precision, backed by a comprehensive, gap-free service history from authorized specialists. This vehicle has been exclusively garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen inclement weather. It comes complete with two original keys, the full owner\u2019s manual suite, and a thick folder of maintenance receipts. If you are looking for a turn-key example that looks and drives exactly as it did on the delivery floor, this is it.",
      "price": 48500.0,
